milestones.description: Chumney and Geoff Barnett's 63-run partnership is CAN's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 59 between Chumney and John Davison
This is the lowest match aggregate (191) involving teams Canada & Kenya in ODIs
John Davison has broken the record for most catches (4) in ODIs for CAN, going past Heaney's 3
Ashish Bagai has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (10) for CAN, going past John Davison
